      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEST FOR PACE (5) is having his first start around this circuit. Recorded his 23rd career win last time out (30.03) at Rockhampton after drawing the same box. Expected to go well again. RITZA ROCKER (7) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 1.5 lengths second over 400m at this track, clocking 23.07. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Expecting another good run. STOCK'S GIFT (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (23.10) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Should be about the money. STYLISH EYES (1) is among the chances again if she runs up to the latest effort.",
